Today Hannah and Gregg IDed that the mouse was licking to changes but not getting rewards so we moved the spout a bit closer (400 in and 200 up). This seems to have reduced the misses but may have increased aborts. We should keep an eye on this - gregg thinks that we should put the lickspout in a positino where it doesn't miss licks; because missing licks fundamentally changes the statistics of the behavior they are being asked to perform.
